statements.sql: select `id`, `ape_paterno`, `ape_materno`, `nombre`, `r`.`estado` as `estado`, `r`.`rude_id` as `CodAlm`, `g`.`gst_aula` as `aula`, `e`.`grd_nombre` as `curso`, `e`.`grd_id` as `idCurso`, `n`.`grd_nivel_id` as `idNivel` from `users` inner join `rude` as `r` on `id` = `r`.`user_id` inner join `rude_1_gestion` as `g` on `id` = `g`.`user_id` and `g`.`gst_gestion` = '2018' inner join `grd_escolar` as `e` on `g`.`gst_grd_escolar` = `e`.`grd_id` inner join `grd_nivel` as `n` on `n`.`grd_nivel_id` = `e`.`grd_orden` where (`tipo_Usu` = 'Est_ccc') order by `e`.`grd_id` asc, `ape_paterno` asc, `ape_materno` asc, `nombre` asc limit 1000

select `g`.`gst_grd_escolar` as `Curso`, `r`.`sexo`, COUNT(r.user_id) as Alums from `rude_1_gestion` as `g` inner join `rude` as `r` on `r`.`user_id` = `g`.`user_id` inner join `rude_1_gestion` as `gest` on `gest`.`user_id` = `r`.`user_id` and `gest`.`gst_gestion` = '2018' inner join `users` as `u` on `id` = `r`.`user_id` inner join `grd_escolar` as `e` on `e`.`grd_id` = `g`.`gst_grd_escolar` inner join `grd_nivel` as `n` on `n`.`grd_nivel_id` = `e`.`grd_orden` group by `g`.`gst_grd_escolar`, `r`.`sexo`

statements.sql:
SELECT  DATE_FORMAT(CAST( u.created_at AS DATE ),"%c-%d") as dia,
COUNT( id ) as total
from   users as u,
rude as r,
rude_1_gestion as g,
grd_escolar as e,
grd_nivel as n
where tipo_Usu="Est_ccc"
and (id=r.user_id)
and (id = g.user_id)
and(g.gst_gestion = 2018)
and (g.gst_grd_escolar = e.grd_id)
and(n.grd_nivel_id = e.grd_orden)
GROUP BY  DATE_FORMAT(CAST( u.created_at AS DATE ),"%c-%d")
